{
  "stem": "9943.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went in Rostov to three gymnasiums because my mother-- it was my mother's-- my mother's initiative that I should start studying in summertime when there is a vacation and skip a class-- and skip a class.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the result was that at the time when we went back to-- home, I was advanced in gymnasium there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was finishing sixth class.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I would have probably graduated-- in a year or two, I would have graduated from high school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when we arrived to-- back home, that shtetl Wlodzimierzec became Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That means that we had to start-- study Polish language in order to, to get to school and to catch up with the difference in the education-- Polish education and the Russian education.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The, the way we went back home is that my, my mother's brother sent papers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He, he was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in Luck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in Luck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when we packed and went-- didn't have much problems getting back to-- back home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went by train to Minsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember in Minsk, we spent a, a, a month waiting for get-- to get together papers, exactly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what we were sitting there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Minsk is Belarussia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Belarus, it's now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, it's a separate-- but it's over, the czars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] We came-- we came back-- we came back in the fall of, of '22.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were in the-- our old house in Wlodzimierzec, the same Wlodzimierzec.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we spent a year there, had the teacher that taught-- we-- three of us girls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't remember whether Mina also was in that group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had the one teacher, all of us, to learn Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She knew Polish German.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
